Why AGPL here?
--------------

This repository depends on `EbookLib`, which is distributed under
AGPLv3+ (GNU Affero General Public License v3 or later).
To map restrictive/copyleft obligations clearly at repository level,
this project is licensed as AGPL-3.0-or-later.

Third-party dependency license mapping
--------------------------------------

- docling: MIT
- easyocr: Apache-2.0
- streamlit: Apache-2.0
- Markdown (python-markdown): BSD-3-Clause
- EbookLib: AGPL-3.0-or-later

The above licenses are compatible with distributing this project under
AGPL-3.0-or-later, while preserving the strongest copyleft requirement.

